==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''cardioid''' (''plural'' '''cardioids''')

#{{geometry}} An [[epicycloid]] with exactly one [[cusp]]; the [[plane curve]] with [[polar equation]] <math>\rho = 1 + \cos\,\theta</math>.

